		<article class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><h1 class="pageTitle" itemprop="name headline">
				School Closings Due To COVID-19 Pandemic
			</h1>
	
		
			<div class="article-content">
			
			
					<div class="body cf">
						<div>With additional cases of Coronavirus Disease (COVID-19) and the potential of community transmission in Dallas County, UME Preparatory Academy is extending Spring Break through March 20, 2020, and will begin home-based instruction for all campuses beginning March 23, 2020 and extending through March 27, 2020. This is an ever-evolving situation, and we will post further updates as well as continue to send emails home to parents as soon as they are made available.</div>
